  chase-welcome          Return to main menu
  theme-selector-terminal Browse and install other editions
  system-info            Show system information
  links <url>            Launch web browser

  Basic Commands:
    ls                   List files
    cd <directory>       Change directory
    pwd                  Show current directory
    nano <file>          Edit text file
    htop                 System monitor (if installed)
    df -h                Disk usage
    free -h              Memory usage
    ip addr              Network interfaces

