  Chase (50MB)     You are here! Minimal and fast
  Pegasus (85MB)   Simplified for elderly users
  Nekomata (120MB) Professional productivity tools
  Hydra (150MB)    Education edition with AI tools
  Dragon (250MB)   Gaming edition with emulators

